# Pass 0116 Ledger: Formal/Physics Source-Lead Bridge

Date: 2026-07-01

## Objective

Convert the four new YouTube leads from pass 0115 into bounded proof-packet
requirements for formal math, quantum foundations, counterexample-driven
research, and looped agent receipts. The pass proves only small finite
identities and receipt mechanics:

- finite-set category identity and associativity;
- two-state Born-rule probability normalization;
- bounded counterexample and revised-claim workflow;
- two-attempt loop replay with external verifier receipts.

No category-theory, physics, theoretical-CS, or agent-reasoning research claim is
promoted beyond `HYPOTHESIS`.

